			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=10940&amp;sid=9a1808a786cbc1e057a1db6ee413d580#p10940"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=10940&amp;sid=9a1808a786cbc1e057a1db6ee413d580#p10940" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#11</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89&amp;sid=9a1808a786cbc1e057a1db6ee413d580" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">Don</a></strong> &raquo; July 15th, 2012, 8:45 am <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

